  "description": "UDP-only same-agent device-credential recovery through an authenticated Hub grant and assigned-cell completion. The recovery credential is the ordinary reusable qurl:agent-scoped credential kind named agent, not a distinct API-key type enum. The existing agent X25519 identity is mandatory; v1 has no takeover path.",
